{"tid":1992851,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【全球關注金正恩，連帶色情網搜尋其妹「金與正」亦大幅增加﹗","createTime":"2020-04-28T11:23:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-28T11:27:33.000Z","uid":37554,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"44bcc454dea4009bfa786173a739255d4a75eca0","tid":1992851,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T11:23:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo?fbid=1695047717310403&amp;set=a.170067379808452\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto%3Ffbid%3D1695047717310403%26set%3Da.170067379808452&d=mbsn9%2Fi9gU9wZYjOUdyYPm0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=503e10cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo?fbid=1695047717310403&amp;set=a.170067379808452</a><br />\n金正恩今天繼續未有公開露面，有關其死訊的謠言如常不斷發酵。<br />\n不少媒體也爭相關注，萬一金正恩真的未能繼續履行職務，他身邊唯一的家族支柱，同屬白頭山血統的妹妹金與正，便成為繼承他權力最有可能的人選之一。<br />\n只是，由於西方媒體對金與正所得的資訊甚少，連她是一個怎樣的人也不了解。這種忽然萌生的好奇心，甚至驅使不少網民，竟然登入全球一大色情影片網站「xHamster」，鍵入她的名字「Kim Yo Jong」，搜尋一切可能有關她的資料。<br />\n據「xHamster」的官方推特帳戶今天發帖，指過去數天，在其網站搜尋「Kim Yo Jong」關鍵語的次數，大幅度上升。<br />\n看來隨著金正恩一直失蹤在公眾目光，金與正受外界注視的程度，將會繼續不斷炒熱。<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/s960x960/94638833_1695047723977069_5996721913785745408_o.jpg?_nc_cat=110&amp;_nc_sid=730e14&amp;_nc_ohc=GflghHSS2rQAX82CPfG&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-1.fna&amp;_nc_tp=7&amp;oh=76bb59043e1ecbf36ea0acec94dff157&amp;oe=5ECF0763\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fs960x960%2F94638833_1695047723977069_5996721913785745408_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D110%26_nc_sid%3D730e14%26_nc_ohc%3DGflghHSS2rQAX82CPfG%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-1.fna%26_nc_tp%3D7%26oh%3D76bb59043e1ecbf36ea0acec94dff157%26oe%3D5ECF0763&h=fb7e3855&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d90a0df0be927c75bbd711ebc21920ae09729480","tid":1992851,"uid":33206,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T11:24:41.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" cla